summary: BLACK SERIES CAMPERS SOLD IN THE USA, COME WITH AN ARTICULATING POLY BLOCK HITCH FROM AUSTRALIA. THESE HITCHES APPEAR TO NOT BE US DOT CERTIFIED. ALSO THE BLACK SERIES POP UP TRAILERS DO NOT COME WITH PROPER TRAILER BREAK-AWAY SYSTEMS, WHICH ARE REQUIRED IN MOST STATES. EXAMPLE PA REQUIRES O. ANY TRAILER OVER 3000# GVWR
